{"tid":2307912,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"清心響應減糖政策！最高糖量「改為少糖」　CEO辯稱全糖沒人點","createTime":"2020-12-01T13:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T14:14:14.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5a15dc0df4f897d13515bda46aad1d4a3d3b50df","tid":2307912,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"為了國人的健康，政府推出減糖政策，希望可以改善民眾肥胖的問題。有網友日前到清心<br />\n福全買飲料，發現店門口貼著一張公告，「為了響應政府的減糖政策，故取消全糖的選項<br />\n，最高糖量改為少糖」。對此，清心福全執行長表示，「此次變動只有單品茶類」。<br />\n <br />\n該名網友在個人臉書貼上一張照片，知名連鎖飲料店為了響應明年政府減糖政策，故將全<br />\n糖取消，最高糖量為少糖。對此，他驚呼「清心竟然不賣全糖了！」<br />\n <br />\n消息一出後，有網友在底下留言，「很好啊！減少健保負擔」。還有網友搞笑回覆，「您<br />\n好，我要一杯QQㄋㄟㄋㄟ好喝到咩噗茶」，此用語出自於一名Youtuber拍攝的一支影片，<br />\n因為現在許多手搖飲的飲料名太特別，加上許多店家冰塊、糖度的標準不一樣，影片一出<br />\n立刻引發網友共鳴，該飲料名甚至成為網路流行用語。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/y3jdhskk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fy3jdhskk&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0gx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=3e5eaf99\" target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/y3jdhskk</a>"},{"pid":"fbf9e5050a92a18c4314f1c7a30baff57b71898b","tid":2307912,"uid":282347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"點解一杯十幾羹糖＋色素嘅垃圾都咁多人趨之若鶩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5acaa5cdeef1d25b0b55f707c2728905984c482f","tid":2307912,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T13:10:53.000Z","msg":"香港有冇分店？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29875f07e8321e49d26b363a3874a8efe3a6815b","tid":2307912,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T13:11:04.000Z","msg":"ChaTraMue先恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c47a02072c6defd80a430baa5c9